// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1476 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 80c16f6e-4e1c-59ac-a47d-ba9dd29e48ee

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
